Paper: hep-th/9611124

Date: 1996-11-17

Title: Simple Current Extensions and Mapping Class Group Representations

Authors: Peter Bantay

Comments: 12 pages, LaTeX, references updated

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A13 (1998) 199-208

The conjecture of Fuchs, Schellekens and Schweigert on the relation ofmapping class group representations and fixed point resolution in simplecurrent extensions is investigated, and a cohomological interpretation of theuntwisted stabilizer is given.